net.cloud.gfx.elements

Class HorizontalView.HorizontalViewElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.gfx.elements.decorator.AbstractDecoratorElement
      • net.cloud.gfx.elements.HorizontalView.HorizontalViewElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DecoratorElement, Element, Focusable
    Enclosing class:
    HorizontalView

    private static class HorizontalView.HorizontalViewElement
extends AbstractDecoratorElement
    Decorator that adds two fields to an element that's been added to the view. It adds alignment and padding. These may or may not be set.
